<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chemical Engineering - GoFarAsYouCan</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
      /* Base Styles */
      :root {
        --primary-color: #0a3d62;        /* Deep teal */
        --primary-light: #3c6382;        /* Lighter teal */
        --secondary-color: #1b263b;      /* Dark navy */
        --accent-color: #5e84ff;         /* Vibrant coral */
        --accent-light: #00f7ff;         /* Soft coral */
        --text-color: #e0e1dd;           /* Soft off-white */
        --light-text: #ffffff;           /* Pure white */
        --light-bg: #415a77;             /* Muted teal background */
        --dark-bg: #0d1b2a;              /* Deep navy background */
        --card-bg: #1b263b;              /* Slightly lighter navy for cards */
        --border-radius: 10px;
        --box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        --transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text-color);
        background-color: var(--light-bg);
        background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-bg) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
        background-attachment: fixed;
      }

      .container {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }

      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--accent-light);
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      a:hover {
        color: #ffd166;
      }

      img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      }

      .bg-light {
        background-color: var(--primary-light);
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-light), var(--secondary-color));
      }

      /* Navbar */
      .navbar {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--light-text);
        padding: 1rem 0;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
      }

      .navbar .container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .back-button a {
        color: var(--light-text);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 5px;
      }

      .back-button a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      /* Hero Section */
      .hero {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--light-text);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 6rem 0;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);
      }

      .hero .overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        opacity: 0.2;
        mix-blend-mode: luminosity;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        position: relative;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        position: relative;
      }

      /* Section Styles */
      .section {
        padding: 5rem 0;
      }

      .section-title {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        color: var(--accent-light);
        position: relative;
        font-size: 2rem;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      }

      .section-title::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 80px;
        height: 4px;
        background-color: var(--accent-light);
        border-radius: 2px;
      }

      .section-intro {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      /* Content Wrapper */
      .content-wrapper {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2.5rem;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .text-content {
        flex: 1;
      }

      .text-content p {
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      .image-content {
        flex: 1;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      /* Cards Grid */
      .cards-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .two-columns {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(450px, 1fr));
      }

      .three-columns {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      }

      .four-columns {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      }

      /* Card Styles */
      .card {
        background-color: var(--card-bg);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        transition: var(--transition);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        border-color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .card-header {
        padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 0.5rem;
        background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(10, 61, 98, 0.3), rgba(207, 94, 255, 0.3));
      }

      .card-header h3 {
        color: var(--accent-light);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      .card-header h3 i {
        color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .card-header p {
        color: #ccc;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .card-content {
        padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem;
      }

      /* Project Cards */
      .project-card .card-image {
        height: 180px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .project-card .card-image img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        transition: transform 0.5s ease;
      }

      .project-card:hover .card-image img {
        transform: scale(1.05);
      }

      /* Career List */
      .career-list {
        list-style: none;
      }

      .career-list li {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .career-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .badge {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        color: #ecf0f1;
        padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .badge.top {
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
        color: white;
      }

      .badge.program {
        background-color: #06d6a0;
        color: white;
      }

      .growth-sectors {
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .text-success {
        color: #ffd166;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      /* Education Pathways */
      .education-pathways {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        background-color: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .education-pathways h3 {
        color: var(--accent-light);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
      }

      .pathways-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .pathway-card {
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .pathway-card:hover {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .pathway-card h4 {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      /* Skills List */
      .skills-list {
        list-style: none;
      }

      .skills-list li {
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .skills-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .skill-name {
        font-weight: 600;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      .skill-desc {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #bdc3c7;
      }

      /* Accordion */
      .accordion {
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .accordion-item {
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .accordion-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .accordion-header {
        padding: 1rem;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 600;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .accordion-header::after {
        content: '\f078';
        font-family: 'Font Awesome 5 Free';
        font-weight: 900;
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .accordion-header.active::after {
        transform: rotate(180deg);
      }

      .accordion-content {
        padding: 0 1rem;
        max-height: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
      }

      .accordion-content p {
        padding-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .accordion-item.active .accordion-header {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .accordion-item.active .accordion-content {
        max-height: 500px;
      }

      /* Specialization Grid */
      .specialization-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(160px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .specialization-card {
        background-color: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        text-align: center;
        transition: var(--transition);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items:center;
        color: var(--text-color);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .specialization-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        background-color: var(--primary-color);
        color: var(--light-text);
        border-color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .specialization-card i {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--accent-light);
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .specialization-card:hover i {
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .specialization-card h3 {
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      /* Internship List */
      .internship-list {
        list-style: none;
      }

      .internship-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .company-name {
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      .company-desc {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #bdc3c7;
      }

      /* Internship Tips */
      .internship-tips {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        background-color: var(--primary-light);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .internship-tips h3 {
        color: var(--accent-light);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
      }

      .tips-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .tips-grid li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .tip-number {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2rem;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--accent-light);
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .tip-title {
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      .tip-desc {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #bdc3c7;
      }

      /* Tabs */
      .tabs {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .tab-buttons {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .tab-button {
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: var(--transition);
        color: var(--text-color);
      }

      .tab-button:first-child {
        border-radius: var(--border-radius) 0 0 var(--border-radius);
      }

      .tab-button:last-child {
        border-radius: 0 var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius) 0;
      }

      .tab-button.active {
        background-color: var(--accent-color);
        color: var(--light-text);
      }

      .tab-content {
        display: none;
      }

      .tab-content.active {
        display: block;
      }

      /* Colleges Grid */
      .colleges-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }

      .college-card {
        background-color: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 1.25rem;
        border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        transition: var(--transition);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      .college-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        border-color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .college-card h3 {
        color: var(--accent-light);
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      }

      .college-location {
        color: #bdc3c7;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .college-details {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        color: #bdc3c7;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .college-rank, .college-year {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      .college-rank i {
        color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .college-year i {
        color: #06d6a0;
      }

      .college-info {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        padding-top: 1rem;
      }

      .college-info p {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .college-info span {
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      /* FAQ Section */
      .faq-container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        background-color: var(--dark-bg);
        color: var(--light-text);
        padding: 4rem 0 1rem;
        background-image: linear-gradient(to top, var(--dark-bg), var(--primary-light));
      }

      .footer-content {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .footer-logo h2 {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .footer-links h3,
      .footer-resources h3 {
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        position: relative;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .footer-links h3::after,
      .footer-resources h3::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 50px;
        height: 3px;
        background-color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .footer-links ul,
      .footer-resources ul {
        list-style-type: none;
      }

      .footer-links li,
      .footer-resources li {
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .footer-links a,
      .footer-resources a {
        color: #bdc3c7;
      }

      .footer-links a:hover,
      .footer-resources a:hover {
        color: var(--accent-light);
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 1.25rem;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      }

      /* Responsive Design */
      @media (max-width: 992px) {
        .content-wrapper {
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .hero h1 {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .two-columns {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section {
          padding: 3.5rem 0;
        }

        .hero {
          padding: 5rem 0;
        }

        .hero h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .section-title {
          font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        .college-details {
          flex-direction: column;
          gap: 0.5rem;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 576px) {
        .navbar {
          padding: 0.75rem 0;
        }

        .logo {
          font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
          font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .section-title {
          font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tab-buttons {
          flex-direction: column;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 300px;
          margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        }

        .tab-button {
          border-radius: 0;
        }

        .tab-button:first-child {
          border-radius: var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius) 0 0;
        }

        .tab-button:last-child {
          border-radius: 0 0 var(--border-radius) var(--border-radius);
        }

        .specialization-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
        }
      }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="logo">GoFarAsYouCan</div>
            <div class="back-button">
                <a href="/Engineering/engineering.ejs"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Chemical Engineering</h1>
            <p>Unlock the power of chemistry to design innovative processes and materials that shape the future</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- What is Chemical Engineering Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Chemical Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Chemical engineering combines principles of chemistry, physics, mathematics, and biology to design processes that convert raw materials into valuable products. From developing sustainable fuels to creating life-saving pharmaceuticals, chemical engineers solve real-world problems on a global scale.</p>
                    <p>As a chemical engineer, you'll work on designing, optimizing, and managing processes in industries like energy, pharmaceuticals, food production, and materials manufacturing. The field requires creativity, analytical thinking, and a passion for innovation to address challenges like sustainability and resource efficiency.</p>
                    <p>Chemical engineering is at the forefront of tackling pressing issues such as renewable energy, clean water, and advanced materials, making it a dynamic and impactful career choice.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Specializations Section -->
    <section class="section bg-light" id="specializations">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Specializations</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Explore exciting specializations within chemical engineering to match your interests and career goals:</p>
            
            <div class="specialization-grid">
                <a href="process.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
                    <h3>Process Engineering</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="biochemical.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-dna"></i>
                    <h3>Biochemical Engineering</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="petroleum.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-oil-can"></i>
                    <h3>Petroleum Engineering</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="polymer.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-atom"></i>
                    <h3>Polymer Engineering</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="environmental.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    <h3>Environmental Engineering</h3>
                </a>
                <a href="nanotech.ejs" class="specialization-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-microscope"></i>
                    <h3>Nanotechnology</h3>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Career Paths Section -->
    <section class="section bg-light" id="careers">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Career Paths & Outlook</h2>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Industry Roles</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <ul class="career-list">
                            <li>
                                <span>Process Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹6-18 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>Plant Manager</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹10-25 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>Environmental Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹5-15 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>R&D Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹7-20 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Job Outlook</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>The demand for chemical engineers in India is expected to grow by 12% through 2030, with opportunities in energy, pharmaceuticals, and sustainable technologies.</p>
                        <div class="growth-sectors">
                            <span class="text-success">Growth Sectors:</span>
                            <ul>
                                <li>• Renewable Energy</li>
                                <li>• Pharmaceuticals</li>
                                <li>• Green Chemistry</li>
                                <li>• Advanced Materials</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
